{"tha-ap18:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap18:0.2":"Sihasaniyavagga ","tha-ap18:0.3":"Rahulattheraapadana ","tha-ap18:1.1":"“Padumuttarassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap18:1.2":"Lokajetthassa tadino; ","tha-ap18:1.3":"Sattabhumamhi pasade, ","tha-ap18:1.4":"Adasam santharim aham. ","tha-ap18:2.1":"Khinasavasahassehi, ","tha-ap18:2.2":"parikinno mahamuni; ","tha-ap18:2.3":"Upagami gandhakutim, ","tha-ap18:2.4":"dvipadindo narasabho. ","tha-ap18:3.1":"Virocento gandhakutim, ","tha-ap18:3.2":"devadevo narasabho; ","tha-ap18:3.3":"Bhikkhusanghe thito sattha, ","tha-ap18:3.4":"ima gatha abhasatha. ","tha-ap18:4.1":"‘Yenayam jotita seyya, ","tha-ap18:4.2":"adasova susanthato; ","tha-ap18:4.3":"Tamaham kittayissami, ","tha-ap18:4.4":"sunatha mama bhasato. ","tha-ap18:5.1":"Sonnamaya rupimaya, ","tha-ap18:5.2":"atho veluriyamaya; ","tha-ap18:5.3":"Nibbattissanti pasada, ","tha-ap18:5.4":"ye keci manaso piya. ","tha-ap18:6.1":"Catusatthikkhattum devindo, ","tha-ap18:6.2":"devarajjam karissati; ","tha-ap18:6.3":"Sahassakkhattum cakkavatti, ","tha-ap18:6.4":"bhavissati anantara. ","tha-ap18:7.1":"Ekavisatikappamhi, ","tha-ap18:7.2":"vimalo nama khattiyo; ","tha-ap18:7.3":"Caturanto vijitavi, ","tha-ap18:7.4":"cakkavatti bhavissati. ","tha-ap18:8.1":"Nagaram renuvati nama, ","tha-ap18:8.2":"itthakahi sumapitam; ","tha-ap18:8.3":"Ayamato tini satam, ","tha-ap18:8.4":"caturassasamayutam. ","tha-ap18:9.1":"Sudassano nama pasado, ","tha-ap18:9.2":"vissakammena mapito; ","tha-ap18:9.3":"Kutagaravarupeto, ","tha-ap18:9.4":"sattaratanabhusito. ","tha-ap18:10.1":"Dasasaddavivittam tam, ","tha-ap18:10.2":"vijjadharasamakulam; ","tha-ap18:10.3":"Sudassanamva nagaram, ","tha-ap18:10.4":"devatanam bhavissati. ","tha-ap18:11.1":"Pabha niggacchate tassa, ","tha-ap18:11.2":"uggacchanteva suriye; ","tha-ap18:11.3":"Virocessati tam niccam, ","tha-ap18:11.4":"samanta atthayojanam. ","tha-ap18:12.1":"Kappasatasahassamhi, ","tha-ap18:12.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap18:12.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap18:12.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap18:13.1":"Tusita so cavitvana, ","tha-ap18:13.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap18:13.3":"Gotamassa bhagavato, ","tha-ap18:13.4":"atrajo so bhavissati. ","tha-ap18:14.1":"Sacevaseyya agaram, ","tha-ap18:14.2":"cakkavatti bhaveyya so; ","tha-ap18:14.3":"Atthanametam yam tadi, ","tha-ap18:14.4":"agare ratimajjhaga. ","tha-ap18:15.1":"Nikkhamitva agaramha, ","tha-ap18:15.2":"pabbajissati subbato; ","tha-ap18:15.3":"Rahulo nama namena, ","tha-ap18:15.4":"araha so bhavissati’. ","tha-ap18:16.1":"Kikiva andam rakkheyya, ","tha-ap18:16.2":"camari viya valadhim; ","tha-ap18:16.3":"Nipako silasampanno, ","tha-ap18:16.4":"evam rakkhim mahamuni. ","tha-ap18:17.1":"Tassaham dhammamannaya, ","tha-ap18:17.2":"vihasim sasane rato; ","tha-ap18:17.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap18:17.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap18:18.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap18:18.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap18:18.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap18:18.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap18:19.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma rahulo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap18:20.1":"Rahulattherassapadanam chattham. "}